Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,A bouncing blue light led a\Ntiny fox beyond the garden gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.00,0:00:10.00,Default,,0,0,0,,In the willow pond, the fox learned that a\Ntiny bird had lost the nest it called home.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.00,0:00:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What began as a rescue mission grew harder\Nwhen the golden button slipped out of reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.00,0:00:20.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The thoughtful fox decided to reach the stranded friend\Nand turned fallen petals into tiny guiding flags.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.00,0:00:25.00,Default,,0,0,0,,The plan worked, bringing a safe\Nrescue for everyone in the willow pond.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.00,0:00:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone laughed as the helpful object gave one joyful bounce.\NThe golden button softly echoed the adventure's beginning.
